about.description: Display Sankey diagrams in Jupyter notebooks, using d3-sankey-diagram.

name: ipysankeywidget
raw_meta_yaml:
{% set name = "ipysankeywidget" %}
{% set version = "0.2.5" %}

package:
  name: {{ name|lower }}
  version: {{ version }}

source:
  url: https://pypi.io/packages/source/{{ name[0] }}/{{ name }}/{{ name }}-{{ version }}.tar.gz
  sha256: 02f710529ccfab002914597afeb731f221e7a29b00238f9fd7ed447b620b90e2

build:
  noarch: python
  number: 0
  script: "{{ PYTHON }} -m pip install . --no-deps -vv"

requirements:
  host:
    - python
    - pip
  run:
    - python
    - ipywidgets >=7.0.0

test:
  imports:
    - ipysankeywidget

about:
  home: http://github.com/ricklupton/ipysankeywidget
  license: MIT
  license_family: MIT
  license_file: LICENCE
  summary: 'IPython / Jupyter Sankey diagram widget'

  description: |
    Display Sankey diagrams in Jupyter notebooks, using d3-sankey-diagram.
  doc_url: https://github.com/ricklupton/ipysankeywidget
  dev_url: https://github.com/ricklupton/ipysankeywidget

extra:
  recipe-maintainers:
    - ricklupton
